premise_source_doc_sentence: Sarrainodu  (  The Right Person  )  is a 2016 Indian Telugu-language action-masala film written and directed by Boyapati Srinu .

Singh was part of the commercially successful Telugu films like Venkatadri Express  (  2013  )  , Current Theega  (  2014  )  and Loukyam  (  2014  )  , leading her to land in bigger projects in the industry like Kick 2  (  2015  )  , Bruce Lee  (  2015  )  , Nannaku Prematho  (  2016  )  , Sarrainodu  (  2016  )  and Dhruva  (  2016  )  .
